next.excerpt:
As always this game is extremely fun and with todays video I decided to switch skins every turn rather than when it's just the boyfriend. I had a little more issue trying to sync the clips together near the end but I managed somehow. Also, I want people to still know that I did use a bot to keep things well sync because I don't intend on hiding that fact since I wanted to make this video as a fun viewing experience while delivering people exposure of new skin mods out there. In addition, I did not cross dissolve transition since one viewer recommended not too since it ruins the flow and while looking at it I have to agree. Even though some character skins didn't get a chance to sing I still made sure to each one gets a different skin while also making them look good in terms of their respected fandom. localize.title: 周五晚上的FUNKIN'--Pico，但每转一圈都会使用不同的皮肤MOD。
localize.description:
一如既往，这个游戏非常有趣，今天的视频我决定每回合都要换皮肤，而不是只有男朋友的时候。我有一个更多的问题，试图同步的剪辑在一起接近结束，但我设法以某种方式。另外，我希望人们仍然知道，我确实使用了一个机器人来保持东西很好的同步，因为我不打算隐藏这个事实，因为我想让这个视频作为一个有趣的观看体验，同时提供人们暴露的新皮肤mods在那里。此外，我没有交叉溶解过渡，因为一个观众建议不要太，因为它破坏了流程，而看着它，我不得不同意。即使一些角色皮肤没有机会唱歌，我仍然确保每个人得到一个不同的皮肤，同时也使他们看起来很好，在他们尊重的影迷。总的来说，又是一个有趣的视频，我希望能再继续一段时间。
